Update 1.4 is here! This time we did some major changes, so be sure to check it out and don't forget to leave a review because your feedback is important!

* Introducing Kickardo, he'll teach you how to freestyle!
* AR mode - juggle the ball wherever you please!
* Redesigned the main menu
* League Mode is now the default mode
* Removed challenge mode, but worry not! It'll be back soon in a new and improved form.
* Level cap increased to 999
* New York is now available for free!
* and many more
